## Usage

### Installation

Install latest from the GitHub
[repository](https://github.com/bilalcodehub/dosagelimitsindex):

``` sh
$ pip install git+https://github.com/bilalcodehub/dosagelimitsindex.git
```

or from [conda](https://anaconda.org/bilalcodehub/dosagelimitsindex)

``` sh
$ conda install -c bilalcodehub dosagelimitsindex
```

or from [pypi](https://pypi.org/project/dosagelimitsindex/)

``` sh
$ pip install dosagelimitsindex
```
